Josette Banzet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josette_Banzet 0 Josette Banzet, Marquise de Bruyenne (born April 6, 1938) is a French-born American-based actress. She won a Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actress in a Series, Miniseries or Television Film for her performance in Rich Man, Poor Man.
